♪Youth passing by in its ignorance♪

182
00:07:29,140 --> 00:07:35,660
♪But I always seem to miss it♪

183
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:39,340
♪I think of those♪

184
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:42,740
♪Promises we made♪

185
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:46,940
♪Like bookmarks in my memory♪

186
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:51,540
♪Flipping through familiar scenes♪

187
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:53,740
♪But those♪

188
00:07:54,260 --> 00:07:57,340
♪Unfulfilled promises♪

189
00:07:57,860 --> 00:08:01,740
♪Are filled with love
that never came true♪

190
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:05,140
♪How can I forget♪

191
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:08,100
Mu Yinan?

192
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:12,470
Mu Yinan?

193
00:08:16,030 --> 00:08:16,710
Yinan?

194
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:18,190
Yinan?

195
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:23,710
Listen,

196
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:27,340
will you stop tormenting yourself?

197
00:09:10,910 --> 00:09:11,990
Mom!

198
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:45,100
♪Time keeps pushing me forward♪

199
00:09:45,540 --> 00:09:49,100
♪To let go of the lingering warmth
of memories♪

200
00:09:50,300 --> 00:09:53,900
♪How hard it is, in a world without you♪

201
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:56,900
♪What's left for me♪

202
00:09:57,580 --> 00:09:59,300
♪Drifting in memories♪

203
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:01,300
♪Only to rediscover♪

204
00:10:01,780 --> 00:10:04,300
♪The galaxy in my eyes♪

205
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,300
♪Filled with regrets♪

206
00:10:06,900 --> 00:10:10,620
♪Returning is fate's
inevitable consequence♪

207
