♪Chance of love is fleeting♪

211
00:10:31,260 --> 00:10:33,100
♪We brush past each other
and miss the chance♪

212
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:37,700
♪When I came to,
I realize the loneliness♪

213
00:10:38,570 --> 00:10:40,300
♪Our moments are so memorable♪

214
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:44,900
♪Every little detail of the memory♪

215
